# 过滤关键词：命中标题或摘要即收录（大小写不敏感，子串匹配）
# 同一行用 AND 连接表示“同时包含”，例如：sensing AND metamaterial
# 命中任一行即收录。

# ── 超材料 / 超表面 核心 ────────────────────────────────
metamaterial
metasurface
metastructure
metalens
metadevice

# ── 可编程 / 可重构 / 智能 ──────────────────────────────
programmable metamaterial
reconfigurable metasurface
intelligent metasurface
reconfigurable intelligent surface

# ── 声/弹性/力学 超材料 ─────────────────────────────────
acoustic metamaterial
elastic metamaterial
mechanical metamaterial

# ── 传感（与超材料/超表面组合）─────────────────────────
sensing AND metamaterial
sensing AND metasurface
sensor AND metasurface
terahertz AND sensing
piezoelectric AND sensor
flexible AND sensor
tactile AND sensor

# ── 传感（通用）────────────────────────────────────────
sensor
sensing
biosensor
wearable

# ── 逆设计 / 机器学习 ───────────────────────────────────
inverse design AND metamaterial
topology optimization AND metamaterial
learned metamaterial
differentiable AND metamaterial

# ── 物理学习 / 物理神经网络 ─────────────────────────────
physical learning
physical neural network
physical learning machine
mechanical neural network
physical reservoir computing
in-materia computing
learning machine AND physical
neuromorphic AND metamaterial
